<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>避坑 - 标签 - 耶利亚</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/tags/%E9%81%BF%E5%9D%91/</link><description>求之不得的目标，需要一生的努力</description><generator>Hugo 0.159.2 &amp; FixIt v0.4.2-20260109063229-50d27e0e</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Feb 2026 07:31:17 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.yeliya.site/tags/%E9%81%BF%E5%9D%91/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>网站搬家咯</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%90%AC%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%AF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Feb 2026 07:31:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%90%AC%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%AF/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>我现在想把站点搬走，想找个能免费部署的地方，要求是不能花钱，免费额度低点没事，于是这几天尝试了国内几乎所有支持免费静态托管的服务商，总结心得，遂成此文，分享给大家。</description></item><item><title>还是使用docker折腾聚宽吧</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 18:02:52 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>聚宽是个大坑，对库版本要求太严格，怎么改都不行，只好用docker来解决了。</description></item><item><title>学习使用聚宽</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BDing/</link><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jan 2026 13:21:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%81%9A%E5%AE%BDing/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>聚宽提供了比较少见的可以免费用一段时间的量化数据集，尤其是可转债数据，聚宽给得比较大方。我先尝试使用一下。</description></item><item><title>国内可用的docker镜像站点</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84docker%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84docker%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>&lt;p&gt;最近在折腾服务器，Docker Hub官方仓库经常连不上，拉取超时、报错 &lt;code&gt;i/o timeout&lt;/code&gt; 等问题，我搜集了一下国内可用的地址，截至2026 年 1 月最新实测可用。这里留一份备查。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Rsync使用笔记</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/rsync%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Jan 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/rsync%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/">学习笔记</category><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="-前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;📖 前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#-%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;说实话，Linux 下文件同步的工具不少，但 Rsync 真的是最稳的那个。增量传输、断点续传、压缩传输，该有的功能都有，而且几乎每个 Linux 系统都自带。这篇记录一下我这些年用 Rsync 的经验，从基础用法到异地容灾。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>20260120最近的思考</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/20260120%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/</link><pubDate>Mon, 19 Jan 2026 18:44:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/20260120%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;一路走来，站点上线快一个月了，重点关注的股票分析得很好，可是没有挣到钱，我要好好反省下自己。这叫自我批评。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Hexo切换到Hugo</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/hexo%E6%8D%A2%E5%88%B0hugo/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Jan 2026 14:39:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/hexo%E6%8D%A2%E5%88%B0hugo/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>建站平台从Hexo换到Hugo了，再也不折腾平台了。</description></item><item><title>误入歧途与绝地求生：一个名字引发的全球 0.3 秒博客架构史</title><link>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%AF%AF%E5%85%A5%E6%AD%A7%E9%80%94%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%9D%E5%9C%B0%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E7%90%830.3%E7%A7%92%E6%9E%81%E9%80%9F%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%8F%B2/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 Dec 2025 18:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yeliya.site/posts/%E8%AF%AF%E5%85%A5%E6%AD%A7%E9%80%94%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%9D%E5%9C%B0%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E7%90%830.3%E7%A7%92%E6%9E%81%E9%80%9F%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%8F%B2/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yeliya.site/categories/%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/">动手实践</category><description>从wordpress选到hexo，从cloudflare看到GitHub pages，还有edgeone。最终实现了全球0.3秒的响应速度。</description></item></channel></rss>